CustomField.description: This field is populated automatically via trigger whenever a product state config record is configured, and that record is the fourth to have "LLC_BI__Is_Booked__c", "LLC_BI__Is_Closed__c", "LLC_BI__Is_Excluded_From_Stage_Duration__c", or "LLC_BI__Is_Ready_To_Transmit__c" enabled for its parent product type. This field stores the stage and status values which make up the state of true for one of the aforementioned checkboxes.
CustomField.label: Value 4
